item.title: Josephine And Her Two Daughters, Part 1
item.description: I had met a nice girl on a chat one evening, Josephine was her name, she was looking for a man and not just a sex date. I had no plans for us to have a relationship, but the fact that she was a petit Asian girl and that she had two daughters, made me play along with the idea of a relationship.
